t proposals and accelerated peer review: <lb/>an observational study. BMC Health Serv. Res. 2015; 15(1): 1-6. <lb/>11. Gallo SA, Carpenter AS, Glisson SR: Teleconference versus face-to-<lb/>face scientific peer review of grant application: effects on <lb/>review outcomes. PLoS One. 2013; 8(8): e71693. <lb/>PubMed Abstract|Publisher Full Text|Free Full Text <lb/></listBibl>

